WEBVTT

00:02:55.813 --> 00:03:00.045
Bio sam jako, jako ozbiljno dete.
(Smeh)

00:03:00.045 --> 00:03:01.950
I tada,

00:03:01.950 --> 00:03:03.384
tokom ranih '90-ih,

00:03:03.384 --> 00:03:07.214
imao sam sopstveno
najsavremenije tehničko oruđe:

00:03:07.214 --> 00:03:09.226
faks.

00:03:09.226 --> 00:03:11.354
I faks je bio oruđe mog aktivizma.

00:03:11.354 --> 00:03:13.202
I u to vreme, to je bio najbolji način

00:03:13.202 --> 00:03:15.097
istovremenog prenosa poruka

00:03:15.097 --> 00:03:17.535
velikim grupama ljudi.

00:03:17.535 --> 00:03:19.981
Daću vam jedan primer 
faks kampanje koju sam vodio.

00:03:19.981 --> 00:03:22.077
Bilo je predvečerje Zalivskog rata

00:03:22.077 --> 00:03:25.358
i ja sam organizovao globalnu 
kampanju plavljenja hotela

00:03:25.358 --> 00:03:26.579
Intekontinental u Ženevi,

00:03:26.579 --> 00:03:28.864
gde su se Džejms Bejker i Tarik Azizi

00:03:28.864 --> 00:03:30.588
sretali pred sam rat,